sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAuth as K8s API (Auth)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant BFF as odh-dashboard (Fastify)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MR as model-registry-ui BFF<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Thanos as Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,BFF: Flow 1: User accesses Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (Cookie/Header)
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS re-encrypt
    KRBAC->>K8sAuth: TokenReview (HTTPS/443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAuth-->>KRBAC: Token valid, user identity
    KRBAC->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview (HTTPS/443)<br/>Can user list projects?
    K8sAuth-->>KRBAC: Authorized
    KRBAC->>BFF: Forward (HTTP/8080, localhost)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User/Groups headers
    BFF-->>KRBAC: React app bundle (static assets)
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard UI

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Dashboard proxies K8s API call

    Browser->>KRBAC: POST /api/k8s/... (HTTPS/8443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KRBAC->>BFF: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User header
    BFF->>K8sAPI: K8s API call (HTTPS/443)<br/>Auth: User token impersonation
    K8sAPI-->>BFF: API response
    BFF-->>KRBAC: Response (HTTP)
    KRBAC-->>Browser: Response (HTTPS)

    Note over Browser,MR: Flow 3: Federated Module Request (Model Registry)

    Browser->>KRBAC: GET /model-registry/api/... (HTTPS/8443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KRBAC->>BFF: Forward to BFF
    BFF->>MR: Proxy (HTTPS/8043)<br/>X-Forwarded-Access-Token header<br/>TLS (service-serving cert)
    MR->>K8sAPI: K8s/Model Registry API (HTTPS/443)<br/>Auth: User token
    K8sAPI-->>MR: Response
    MR-->>BFF: Response (HTTPS)
    BFF-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Browser: Response (HTTPS)

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 4: Prometheus Metrics Query

    Browser->>KRBAC: GET /api/prometheus/... (HTTPS/8443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KRBAC->>BFF: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    BFF->>Thanos: Query (HTTPS/9092)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Thanos-->>BFF: Metrics data
    BFF-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Browser: Metrics response (HTTPS)
